image dataurl=null mode="contain"
| render

image dataurl={asset "asset-9e9608d5-9432-4d4c-8fea-afe4e461eb57"} mode="contain"

kibana
| essql query="
    SELECT ID.keyword 
    FROM \"issues_github\"
  "
| markdown "There are currently **{{rows.length}}** issues tagged with the chosen theme.
"

}"

kibana
| selectFilter
| demodata
| markdown 
  "The following Metrics display the number of tickets tagged as High/Normal/Low priority."
| render

kibana
| selectFilter
| essql query="SELECT \"Priority.keyword\" FROM \"issues_github\""
| pointseries x="size(Priority.keyword)" y="Priority.keyword" color="Priority.keyword"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle bars=0.75 horizontalBars=true color="#00AEEF"} legend=false palette={palette "#7ECAE3" "#003A4D" gradient=true} seriesStyle={seriesStyle color="#000000"}
| render

kibana
| selectFilter
| esdocs index="issues_github" fields="Priority.keyword" query="Priority.keyword:High"
| math "size(Priority.keyword)"
| metric 
  metricFont={font align="left" color="#00AEEF" family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" italic=false size=30 underline=false weight="normal"} 
  labelFont={font align="left" color="#FFFFFF" family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" italic=false size=14 underline=false weight="bold"} metricFormat="0,0.[000]"
| render

  labelFont={font align="center" color="#777777" family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" italic=false size=14 underline=false weight="normal"} metricFormat="0,0.[000]"

{{#each rows}}

{{/each}}
"
